StringValues.16: A rumor of the long-vanished mace master, Mi Krau-Li.

Pages.Text: In the days when Isparians were new to Dereth, one of the courageous heroes who defended our people against Dereth's monsters was a jitte-wielder of great skill named Mi Krau-Li. He was obsessed with the creation of the "perfect" jitte. Mi Krau-Li disappeared into the hills southwest of Fort Witshire, around 17.3N 32.8E, shortly before the appearance of the first lifestones.
